SQL_STMT_U.val: select CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO, CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO, case when DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH=0 then DEBH_NO else DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH end as DEBTOR, min(DEBC_NO) from :1/DEBC join :1/CLNT on CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT <> 2 and CLNT402_ADVANCE > 0 and CLNT212_INVOICEBUYING = 'Y' join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = DEBC_ADMNO and ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' and ADMN_TESTCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN_ENDCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN_SUPPLYCHAINFINANCE = 'N' join :1/DEBB on DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and DEBB_ACTINVAFACACCH > 0 join :1/DEBH on DEBH_NO = DEBC_DEBH and DEBH_NO > 2 where DEBC_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DEBC_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and DEBC_DATDELETED is null group by CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO, CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO, case when DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH=0 then DEBH_NO else DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH end order by CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO, CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO, case when DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH=0 then DEBH_NO else DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH end for fetch only

select cast(sum(DCMC_SPECIALACCOUNTH) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/DCMC join :1/CLNT on CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO = :3 join :1/DEBH on :4 and DEBH_DATDELETED is null join :1/DEBC on DEBC_DEBH = DEBH_NO and DEBC_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DEBC_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and DEBC_DATDELETED is null where DCMC_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and DCMC_MARK_CODE = :5 for fetch only

select cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE) / case when sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) <> 0 then sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) else 1 end as decimal(5,0)) from :1/DCMO join :1/CLNT on CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO = :3 join :1/DEBH on :4 and DEBH_DATDELETED is null join :1/DEBC on DEBC_DEBH = DEBH_NO and DEBC_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DEBC_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and DEBC_DATDELETED is null where DCMO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':5' and DCMO_MONTHNUMBER between :6 and :7 for fetch only

select max(DEBB_DATLASTPAYMENTRECV) from :1/DEBB join :1/CLNT on CLNT107_LIMITS_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT107_LIMITS_CLNTNO = :3 join :1/DEBH on :4 and DEBH_DATDELETED is null join :1/DEBC on DEBC_DEBH = DEBH_NO and DEBC_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DEBC_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and DEBC_DATDELETED is null where DEBB_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO for fetch only

select INVO_NO, INVO_ADMNO, INVO_CLNTNO, INVO_DEBC_NO, INVO_AACTUALC, CLNT108_ACC_CURR from :1/INVO join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = INVO_ADMNO and ADMN_SUPPLYCHAINFINANCE = 'N' join :1/CLNT on CLNT101_ADMNO = INVO_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = INVO_CLNTNO and CLNT212_INVOICEBUYING = 'Y' join :1/DEBC on DEBC_NO = INVO_DEBC_NO and DEBC_LEGALCOLLECTION = 'N' join :1/INVA on INVA_NO = INVO_NO and INVA_CURRENCY = INVO_CURRENCY and INVA_ACTAFACTORING > 0 exception join :1/IMQI on IMQI_INVO_NO = INVO_NO where INVO_MAXFINANCETIMPASSED is null and days(INVO_DUEDATE) + CLNT407_WITHOUTRECOURSE <= days(':2')+10 and INVO_AACTUALI > 0 and INVO_CODDRAFT = 'N' and INVO_MARKCODETEXT <> :3 for fetch only
update :1/MQHI set MQHI_INVO_NO = 1 where MQHI_MQTY_ID in (273, 274) and MQHI_INVO_NO = 0 and not(exists(select * from :1/MQDT where MQDT_MQTY_ID = MQHI_MQTY_ID and MQDT_DEBC_NO = MQHI_DEBC_NO))
select IMQI_IMQH_ADMNO, IMQI_IMQH_CLNTNO, IMQI_IMQH_TYPE, IMQI_LINENO, IMQI_INVO_NO from :1/IMQI, :1/INVO where IMQI_IMQH_TYPE = 10 and IMQI_INVO_NO = INVO_NO and INVO_AACTUALI = 0 for fetch only

select count(*), cast(sum(INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/IMQI, :1/INVO where IMQI_INVO_NO = INVO_NO and IMQI_IMQH_ADMNO = :2 and IMQI_IMQH_CLNTNO = :3 and IMQI_IMQH_TYPE = :4 and IMQI_LINENO = :5 for fetch only
